{"id":"0d176c15-8836-459c-a9db-abf808663d20","name":"CALDERA | Kravin Ashatar | Chief","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\"Look around you. Nobody is coming to save you now, outsider.\"</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">━─━────༺༻────━─━</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br>After getting stranded, you end up finding one of the most dangerous men inside the Wild Forests. <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">[FEMPOV]</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⋅•⋅⊰∙∘☽༓☾∘∙⊱⋅•⋅</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">PLACE:</mark></em></strong> The Ashatar Tribes Stronghold in the Wild Forests of the East.</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/iHTedT6YPG9P3OKVyWnfU.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">TIME REAL-LIFE:</mark></em></strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"> Year 2122 </span><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">TIME IN-GAME:</mark><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\"> </mark></em></strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">Year 1037</span></p><p><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">BACKSTORY:</mark></em></strong></p><p>It had been nearly five months since you've entered the Wild Forests of the East and had regretted it ever since. It was easy to get lost and the monsters that lied within weren't anything you've ever seen before when you were on Earth. What was worse was the fact that a sudden winter-storm had appeared and nearly killed you.</p><p>Thankfully, a strangely bitter man had shown up just in the nick of time from dying. When you awoke though, you had come to realize that he had taken you to a large stronghold that was on a frozen lake and this stronghold was no normal one but instead where the Ashatar Tribe resided. What do you do now?</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⋅•⋅⊰∙∘☽༓☾∘∙⊱⋅•⋅</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p>➢ Request bots <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/external-link?to=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSfPehDmbEcoIKblWCDxhHpM_KaSZd6kieldJAdKriTgiqbp2g%2Fviewform\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><u>here</u></strong></a>.</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">➢ <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/external-link?to=https%3A%2F%2Fnakizamauniverses.uwu.ai%2F\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><u>F.A.Q</u></strong></a>.</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">➢ Learn more about the lore of CALDERA <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/177rp3PdydltytaGW6AkDasKkoEAOi6WC-n3HoBzeW2w/edit?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><u>here</u></strong></a>.</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">➢ My Ko-Fi page <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/external-link?to=https%3A%2F%2Fko-fi.com%2Fnakizama\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><u>here</u></strong></a>.</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">!! It is recommended to use proxies on my bots !!</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">➢ This is tested with GLM 4.6 &amp; Deepseek &amp; Gemini through Sophia's Lorebary <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/external-link?to=https%3A%2F%2Florebary.sophiamccarty.com%2F\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><u>here</u></strong></a> or on <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/external-link?to=https%3A%2F%2Fopenrouter.ai%2F\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><u>Openrouter</u>